# ****RST

`The RST is an app intended to help organize all the sales that take place in my workplace`
`We often find ourselves a little overwhelmed keeping track of all the open orders, This app aims to help that problem`

`It will Display budgets and amounts shipped month to date. It will automatically calculate the shipped amounts and remaining amounts that need to be shipped.`
